  "2026-07-18T12:18:13.064Z",maintainer-agent,"Duplicate check 2026-07-18: all-status AND searches for post-install activation module cache and reinstall overwrite activation stale export found no canonical item. Related closed cache-reset lineage pm-8fxc covers invocation snapshot state, not ESM dependency cache during same-process overwrite; package lifecycle primitive lineage is pm-x6jf. Finding came from required latest pm-changelog generation and was proven not to be a pm-changelog package defect by published tarball hashes/exports plus fresh-process doctor activation."
